  "siteName": "Vercel News",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack article_content__xNUGz\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:24px\" data-customer-story=\"false\">\n   <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack w-full flex-wrap gap-4\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:row;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:space-between;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\">\n    <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:row;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:6px\">\n     <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-900);--text-size:0.875rem;--text-line-height:1.25rem;--text-letter-spacing:0px;--text-weight:400\"><br></p></div></div>\n   <div class=\"article_leadIn__vSmkA\">\n    <p>From optimized core web vitals to integrated analytics, understand how v0 creates SEO-ready deployments by default</p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Building for the web goes beyond speed and aesthetics, discoverability matters just as much. While AI can accelerate web development, it often skips over performance, accessibility, or SEO best practices that matter for discoverability. With <a href=\"https://v0.dev\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">v0</a>, you don’t have to compromise. Every interface you generate is fast, accessible, and SEO-optimized by default.</p>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">v0 integrates with Next.js and deploys to Vercel, giving you<!-- --> structured metadata, performance tuning, and <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/frameworks/nextjs#server-side-rendering-ssr\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">Server Side Rendering</a> (SSR). The result is better <a href=\"https://developers.google.com/search/docs/appearance/core-web-vitals\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">Core Web Vitals</a>, pages that load quickly and return full HTML, making them easier for search engines to crawl and index.</p>\n   <h2 class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_subheading__5II6M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1.5rem;--xs-text-line-height:2rem;--xs-text-weight:600;--xs-text-letter-spacing:-0.96px;--sm-text-size:1.5rem;--sm-text-line-height:2rem;--sm-text-weight:600;--sm-text-letter-spacing:-0.96px;--smd-text-size:2rem;--smd-text-line-height:2.5rem;--smd-text-weight:600;--smd-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px;--md-text-size:2rem;--md-text-line-height:2.5rem;--md-text-weight:600;--md-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px;--lg-text-size:2rem;--lg-text-line-height:2.5rem;--lg-text-weight:600;--lg-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px\"><a class=\"text_subheadingAnchor__eW51P\" href=\"#seo-optimized-from-your-first-prompt\" id=\"seo-optimized-from-your-first-prompt\">SEO-optimized from your first prompt \n     <svg class=\"text_hash__wLjCi\" data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg></a></h2>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Good SEO starts with performance. Google uses Core Web Vitals to measure how real users experience your site, focusing on loading speed, responsiveness, and layout shift. v0 generates code that automatically applies Next.js optimizations to improve these signals, including:</p>\n   <ul class=\"text_unorderedList__Ivoe0\">\n    <li class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M text_listItem__JyZKR\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Native <a href=\"https://nextjs.org/docs/pages/building-your-application/optimizing/images\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">image optimization</a> with <code>next/image</code></p></li>\n    <li class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M text_listItem__JyZKR\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"><a href=\"https://nextjs.org/docs/app/building-your-application/optimizing/fonts\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">Font optimization</a> without layout shifts</p></li>\n    <li class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M text_listItem__JyZKR\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Smart JavaScript bundling and prefetching</p></li>\n   </ul>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">This gives your site the technical foundation to support instant page loads, low blocking time, and a consistent visual experience, all key factors for ranking higher in search results.</p>\n   <h3 class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_subheading2__6ABHL\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:600;--xs-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:600;--sm-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:600;--smd-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:600;--md-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--lg-text-size:1.25rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.625rem;--lg-text-weight:600;--lg-text-letter-spacing:-0.4px\"><a class=\"text_subheadingAnchor__eW51P\" href=\"#metadata-done-right\" id=\"metadata-done-right\">Metadata done right \n     <svg class=\"text_hash__wLjCi\" data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg></a></h3>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">v0 includes built-in support for metadata and structured data using Next.js conventions. Pages come preconfigured with tags that improve how your site appears in search results and social previews.</p>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Every deployment includes:</p>\n   <ul class=\"text_unorderedList__Ivoe0\">\n    <li class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M text_listItem__JyZKR\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">SEO-friendly title and meta description management</p></li>\n    <li class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M text_listItem__JyZKR\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Automatic Open Graph and Twitter Card generation</p></li>\n    <li class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M text_listItem__JyZKR\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">JSON-LD support for rich snippets in search</p></li>\n   </ul>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Without this metadata, search engines may rank your site lower or display it with missing context. v0 handles it for you from the start.</p>\n   <h3 class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_subheading2__6ABHL\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:600;--xs-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:600;--sm-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:600;--smd-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:600;--md-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--lg-text-size:1.25rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.625rem;--lg-text-weight:600;--lg-text-letter-spacing:-0.4px\"><a class=\"text_subheadingAnchor__eW51P\" href=\"#mobile-first,-responsive-by-design\" id=\"mobile-first,-responsive-by-design\">Mobile-first, responsive by design \n     <svg class=\"text_hash__wLjCi\" data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg></a></h3>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">v0 generates designs that are optimized for mobile. Every layout adapts fluidly across screen sizes, using responsive design patterns that work on phones, tablets, and desktops. Google prioritizes mobile usability in it's index, and with v0, you don't need to configure breakpoints or refactor components. The responsiveness is built in from the start.</p>\n   <h3 class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_subheading2__6ABHL\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:600;--xs-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:600;--sm-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:600;--smd-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:600;--md-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--lg-text-size:1.25rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.625rem;--lg-text-weight:600;--lg-text-letter-spacing:-0.4px\"><a class=\"text_subheadingAnchor__eW51P\" href=\"#accessibility-as-a-ranking-signal\" id=\"accessibility-as-a-ranking-signal\">Accessibility as a ranking signal \n     <svg class=\"text_hash__wLjCi\" data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg></a></h3>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Search engines rely on semantic structure to understand and index content. v0 outputs accessible components that follow modern standards, using proper HTML tags, <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">ARIA attributes</a>, and labels. This improves how crawlers interpret your site and how users navigate it with assistive technology. Accessibility improves usability, and it directly supports better SEO.</p>\n   <h2 class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_subheading__5II6M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1.5rem;--xs-text-line-height:2rem;--xs-text-weight:600;--xs-text-letter-spacing:-0.96px;--sm-text-size:1.5rem;--sm-text-line-height:2rem;--sm-text-weight:600;--sm-text-letter-spacing:-0.96px;--smd-text-size:2rem;--smd-text-line-height:2.5rem;--smd-text-weight:600;--smd-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px;--md-text-size:2rem;--md-text-line-height:2.5rem;--md-text-weight:600;--md-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px;--lg-text-size:2rem;--lg-text-line-height:2.5rem;--lg-text-weight:600;--lg-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px\"><a class=\"text_subheadingAnchor__eW51P\" href=\"#powered-by-vercel-infrastructure-and-tooling\" id=\"powered-by-vercel-infrastructure-and-tooling\">Powered by Vercel infrastructure and tooling \n     <svg class=\"text_hash__wLjCi\" data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg></a></h2>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">When you deploy a v0 project, it runs on a platform optimized for global performance and reliability. With automatic edge caching, real-time <a href=\"https://nextjs.org/docs/app/building-your-application/data-fetching/incremental-static-regeneration\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">Incremental Static Regeneration</a> (ISR), and privacy-friendly analytics, your sites stay fast, available, and easy to monitor all while maintaining SEO integrity.</p>\n   <h3 class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_subheading2__6ABHL\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:600;--xs-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:600;--sm-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:600;--smd-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:600;--md-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--lg-text-size:1.25rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.625rem;--lg-text-weight:600;--lg-text-letter-spacing:-0.4px\"><a class=\"text_subheadingAnchor__eW51P\" href=\"#server-side-rendering-by-default\" id=\"server-side-rendering-by-default\">Server Side Rendering by default \n     <svg class=\"text_hash__wLjCi\" data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg></a></h3>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">v0 uses the Next.js App Router and Server Components out of the box. Your deployed websites are server-rendered by default, with full HTML returned at the time of the request, giving crawlers direct access to real content and improves how quickly your site gets indexed.</p>\n   <figure class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_media__17gkA\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:center;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:16px\">\n    <img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"SSR allows you to render pages dynamically on the server.\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"378\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image_intrinsic__ulrJk blog-mode-dependent-media_addPadding__lfHNN blog-mode-dependent-media_notScreenshot__QVv9c image_lightMode__SmqSs\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://assets.vercel.com/image/upload/contentful/image/e5382hct74si/3Zr9amDZHbHlGwvjeSK3ti/70fabd80e20621f77fd12be30f0e1e96/image.png, https://assets.vercel.com/image/upload/contentful/image/e5382hct74si/3Zr9amDZHbHlGwvjeSK3ti/70fabd80e20621f77fd12be30f0e1e96/image.png\" src=\"https://assets.vercel.com/image/upload/contentful/image/e5382hct74si/3Zr9amDZHbHlGwvjeSK3ti/70fabd80e20621f77fd12be30f0e1e96/image.png\">\n    <figcaption class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK blog-media_caption__fNFzJ\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-900);--text-size:0.875rem;--text-line-height:1.25rem;--text-letter-spacing:initial;--text-weight:400;--text-align:center\">\n     SSR allows you to render pages dynamically on the server.\n    </figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">SSR brings two major advantages:</p>\n   <ul class=\"text_unorderedList__Ivoe0\">\n    <li class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M text_listItem__JyZKR\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Faster initial load and first paint for users</p></li>\n    <li class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M text_listItem__JyZKR\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">\n     <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Stronger scores in Google’s page experience metrics like <a href=\"https://developer.chrome.com/docs/lighthouse/performance/lighthouse-largest-contentful-paint\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">Largest Contentful Paint</a> (LCP) and <a href=\"https://developers.google.com/search/blog/2023/05/introducing-inp\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">Interaction to Next Paint</a> (INP)</p></li>\n   </ul>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Because your site runs on Vercel’s <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/edge-network\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">Global Edge Network</a>, both users and crawlers get the fastest response possible, regardless of location.</p>\n   <h3 class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_subheading2__6ABHL\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:600;--xs-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:600;--sm-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:600;--smd-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:600;--md-text-letter-spacing:-0.32px;--lg-text-size:1.25rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.625rem;--lg-text-weight:600;--lg-text-letter-spacing:-0.4px\"><a class=\"text_subheadingAnchor__eW51P\" href=\"#built-in-analytics,-no-third-party-scripts\" id=\"built-in-analytics,-no-third-party-scripts\">Built-in analytics, no third-party scripts \n     <svg class=\"text_hash__wLjCi\" data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"width:12px;height:12px;color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg></a></h3>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Deploying to Vercel from v0 includes access to <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/analytics\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">Vercel Analytics</a> and <a href=\"https://vercel.com/docs/speed-insights\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_self\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">Speed Insights</a>, giving you a look into real user behavior without relying on invasive trackers or third-party cookies. Unlike legacy platforms that compromise privacy for data collection, Vercel’s approach is fully server-side and GDPR compliant by design.</p>\n   <figure class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_media__17gkA\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:center;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:16px\">\n    <img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"A snapshot of the Speed Insights tab from the project view.\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"678\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image_intrinsic__ulrJk blog-mode-dependent-media_addPadding__lfHNN blog-mode-dependent-media_notScreenshot__QVv9c image_lightMode__SmqSs\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://assets.vercel.com/image/upload/contentful/image/e5382hct74si/7r7znmO3TDQuT3WS5zhGWc/54520cb9d737796ee4e7d5d0dd350cc1/res-chart-light.png, https://assets.vercel.com/image/upload/contentful/image/e5382hct74si/7r7znmO3TDQuT3WS5zhGWc/54520cb9d737796ee4e7d5d0dd350cc1/res-chart-light.png\" src=\"https://assets.vercel.com/image/upload/contentful/image/e5382hct74si/7r7znmO3TDQuT3WS5zhGWc/54520cb9d737796ee4e7d5d0dd350cc1/res-chart-light.png\">\n    <figcaption class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK blog-media_caption__fNFzJ\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-900);--text-size:0.875rem;--text-line-height:1.25rem;--text-letter-spacing:initial;--text-weight:400;--text-align:center\">\n     A snapshot of the Speed Insights tab from the project view.\n    </figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Measure key SEO signals like Core Web Vitals, page load times, and bounce rates in real time. Because the data reflects real-world usage across devices, you get a clear picture of how Google sees your site.</p>\n   <h2 class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_subheading__5II6M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1.5rem;--xs-text-line-height:2rem;--xs-text-weight:600;--xs-text-letter-spacing:-0.96px;--sm-text-size:1.5rem;--sm-text-line-height:2rem;--sm-text-weight:600;--sm-text-letter-spacing:-0.96px;--smd-text-size:2rem;--smd-text-line-height:2.5rem;--smd-text-weight:600;--smd-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px;--md-text-size:2rem;--md-text-line-height:2.5rem;--md-text-weight:600;--md-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px;--lg-text-size:2rem;--lg-text-line-height:2.5rem;--lg-text-weight:600;--lg-text-letter-spacing:-1.28px\"><a class=\"text_subheadingAnchor__eW51P\" href=\"#start-building\" id=\"start-building\">Start building \n     <svg class=\"text_hash__wLjCi\" data-testid=\"geist-icon\" height=\"16\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"color:currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\">\n      <path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.46968 1.46968C10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 -0.203923 14.5303 1.46968C16.2039 3.14329 16.2039 5.85674 14.5303 7.53034L12.0303 10.0303L10.9697 8.96968L13.4697 6.46968C14.5575 5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 13.4697 2.53034C12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 1.44252 9.53034 2.53034L7.03034 5.03034L5.96968 3.96968L8.46968 1.46968ZM11.5303 5.53034L5.53034 11.5303L4.46968 10.4697L10.4697 4.46968L11.5303 5.53034ZM1.46968 14.5303C3.14329 16.2039 5.85673 16.204 7.53034 14.5303L10.0303 12.0303L8.96968 10.9697L6.46968 13.4697C5.38186 14.5575 3.61816 14.5575 2.53034 13.4697C1.44252 12.3819 1.44252 10.6182 2.53034 9.53034L5.03034 7.03034L3.96968 5.96968L1.46968 8.46968C-0.203923 10.1433 -0.203925 12.8567 1.46968 14.5303Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n     </svg></a></h2>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">With v0 and Vercel, SEO is not something you add later. It’s built into the way pages are rendered, served, and measured. Every deployment uses server-rendered HTML, optimized assets, and structured metadata to meet modern search standards. You don’t need to configure plugins, manage tags, or stitch together third-party tools.</p><p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"></p>\n  </div>\n \n",
